text: Britt Annica Westerberg (born 25 January 1953) is a Swedish equestrian. She competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Sweden Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Linköping
